        <ul>
            <li>9. You are entitled to cancel your purchase of and return your Ticket(s) at any time prior to the scheduled date of the Event to which the Ticket(s) apply by contacting the us or our customer service team (whichever is expedient) and arranging such cancellation and return, subject to the following:</li>
