            <li>9.1.2.2. for Ticket(s) returned up to 60 days prior to the event date, a reasonable cancellation charge of 30% (thirty percent) will apply;</li>
            <li>9.1.1.3. for Ticket(s) returned up to 40 days prior to the event date, a reasonable cancellation charge of 50% (fifty percent) will apply;</li>
            <li>9.1.1.4. for Ticket(s) returned less than 30 days prior to the event date, a reasonable cancellation charge of 100% (one hundred percent) will apply;</li>
