            <li>9.1.1.6. You hereby acknowledge and agree that the aforementioned cancellation charges constitute reasonable charges.</li>
            <li>9.1.1.7. Notwithstanding the above, if you can provide us with proof that the person for whom, or whose benefit a Ticket was purchased will not be able to attend the Event because of his or her death or hospitalization, no cancellation fee will apply in respect of that Ticket.</li>
            <li>9.1.1.8 If you cancel your purchase of and return your Ticket(s) within 7 (seven) days of purchase, you will be entitled to a full refund of the face value of the ticket;</li>
